author: desruisseaux
msg: WKT 2: replace all-lower case axis names by camel case axis names when the name is known.
Axis names are not really free text. They are specified by ISO 19111 and ISO 19162.
SIS does not put restriction on axis names, but we nevertheless try to use a unique name when we recognize it.
